1. The FileReader class is from which of the following Java packages?
Ans: java.io

2. The _____ method of the Paths class allows you to put together the location
    and the name of the file without having to worry about slashes as separators.
Ans: get()

3. Which of the following is a main class that you can use to stream the content
  of an XML file from the Internet?
Ans:
URL
InputStream
BufferedInputStream
